# Commit Message Attribution Policy

When creating or editing git commit messages for this project:

- Do not include any attribution line indicating Cursor, AI, LLMs, or assistants created the commit.
- Do not add trailers or footer lines such as:
  - `Made-with: Cursor`
  - `Generated by AI`
  - `Co-authored-by: Cursor`
  - Any equivalent attribution text

Allowed commit messages should only describe the change intent and context.

Before finalizing a commit message, remove any AI/Cursor attribution footer if present.
